title: DDFP 616: Week 11 Red Challenge Flag picks & Best WR groups
itunes:title: DDFP 616: Week 11 Red Challenge Flag picks & Best WR groups
description:
Dave Dameshek is joined by Matt Harmon and Matt "Franchise" Franciscovich to discuss the best WR groups in the league (22:10) as well as Franchise's Week 11 Trade Calls (28:02). Also, Ike Taylor and Oakland Raiders CB T.J. Carrie joined Shek to kibitz about T.J.'s upcoming game in Mexico City vs the Patriots (49:12). Then, EmmaVP reads her Week 11 "TV Guide" sci-fi edition game previews for the guys to break down and make their Red Challenge Flag picks (39:35).

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
